             was indicted for <rs id="t18200412-154-off887" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18200412-154-off887" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200412-154-off887" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18200412-154-cd888" type="crimeDate">3d of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200412-154-off887 t18200412-154-cd888"></join>, one pocket-book, value 6 s., and 8 s. 6 d. in monies numbered, the goods and monies of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18200412-154-victim1522" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Bryant
                        <interp inst="t18200412-154-victim1522" type="surname" value="Bryant"></interp>
