                     <interp inst="t18200412-154-person1524" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I picked the pocket-book up near the spot where the prisoner threw it down.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18200412-154-person1525">
                  JOHN 
                  LINES
