                  </persName>
            . I was constable of the night. I took the prisoner in charge. The prosecutor appeared quite sensible to me.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. A man stopped me, and the prosecutor came up and said I was the man.</p>
